**Simplified Text:**

The Collectors Amanda Roy writes about the things she collects and the reasons why people enjoy collecting. Collecting is a world of passion, envy and enthusiasm and delight. However, if you enter this world, remember one thing: you must fall in love with an object before you collect it. People have been collecting things since the beginning of time. Some people collect stones and seashells just for the beauty of their forms and colours. Others collect flowers, paintings or pottery. If you are interested in collecting, there are many things you can collect. You do not have to be rich and powerful to start a collection. You can collect items as different as tulip bulbs and china cups. As small objects become a popular collector's item, so they begin to rise in price.<eos>
